{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a100171c2","title":"张春桥姚文元与广播事业局《毛泽东思想战斗团》的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"73db6bd1dd","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":11,"articleId":"7a100171c2"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"471a503675","name":"张春桥","type":"人物"},{"id":"92a8a42842","name":"姚文元","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"yaowenyuan","name":"姚文元文录","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"姚文元","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/姚文元文录.pdf"},{"id":"zhangchunqiao","name":"春桥文录","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张春桥","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/zhangchunqiao.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"45f848c5df","name":"姚文元"},{"id":"fae13ac6b9","name":"张春桥"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"51dd6b71aa","type":"title","text":"张春桥姚文元与广播事业局《毛泽东思想战斗团》的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"637e6d9248","type":"authors","text":"张春桥姚文元","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"614b6c6add","type":"appellation","text":"〖按：一九六六年十月十八日，《毛泽东思想战斗团》从资产阶级反动路线的白色恐怖中冲杀出来，大造梅益、丁莱夫等一小撮走资派的反。丁莱夫为了维持梅丁王朝的反动统治，扑灭革命的烈火，操纵《誓死纵队》和《红色造反团》，围剿革命派。在我们斗争最艰苦，最激烈的时刻，十二月十一日下午，毛主席司令部派张春桥、姚文元同志来我局，接见了《毛泽东思想战斗团》的十五名代表。张春桥、姚文元同志和代表们亲切交谈了三个多小时，对《毛泽东思想战斗团》的革命行动表示支持。下面是这次接见的谈话纪要。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"ad0e85692d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我们想了解一下情况，找你们党委谈过。我们知道你们有好几个群众组织，基本上有三个，我们都想谈一下，先和你们谈。我们了解过一些情况，但不很多。你们各派都写过信。你们看有什么问题，有什么困难，打算怎么做，或者你们认为需要的，我们都想了解。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"05c6935f6f","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：就这样吧，你们说，我们听。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a83f8b2508","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：要不要先挨个介绍一下？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"d346232811","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：介绍一下吧，你们哪几个是主要负责的？","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"b425202ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们有没有团委呀？","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"cc8da40a48","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，我们只有联络员。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"8a88db520b","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫的“七 · 二九”黑报告，当谈到丁莱夫说群众批评他是“鸡蛋里头挑骨头” 时）","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"1c2a370225","type":"paragraph","text":"张：这是谁说的？丁莱夫？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a75baa0809","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：对。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"46728fb4c9","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫搞假选举阴谋）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e611dc4727","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那你们局里现在还没有选举文革委员会？","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"912269def8","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，还是旧文革领导。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"7f90299aec","type":"paragraph","text":"张：是指定的，还是选举的？","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"4a521b9bf9","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：选举的，但实际上是指定的，基本上是局党委和各大口负责人。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"be42590108","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫在广播学院事件上，对抗中央文革的罪行。谈到丁说“不能说一千二百人都是右派”时）","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"9ed4dfec88","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那时特别对一千二百人讲了话，说你们是受蒙蔽的，包括工作组的大多数，都是好的。我们再三讲。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"9f1c2e36bf","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：他根本没有传达这些。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"451b9309d1","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报局文革迫害鲁迅的儿子周海婴。当谈到有人问周海婴去南方干什么时）","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"4d5e555676","type":"paragraph","text":"张：是不是丁莱夫直接问的？","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"c8c7240fc7","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表介绍情况）","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"5c75983dee","type":"paragraph","text":"张：丁莱夫说他不知道周海婴是中央文革派去的。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"28dc74e8b8","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：他们对周海婴采取了什么行动？","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"38003bdcfb","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：准备开斗争会，会议程序，口号都拟好了。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"2b8ad1c115","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报斗争梅益情况）","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"1fae6171e2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：梅益开了几天会？","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"2d834a48fb","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：四天。后转入小会。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"1fe008f2f7","type":"paragraph","text":"张：有材料可以给我们看，因为情况很多，先谈当前情况。政训队呀，软禁室呀，都是怎么回事？都解决了没有？现在还存在吗？","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"92583101f3","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表介绍政训队情况）","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"3145fc21e4","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政训队有多少人？","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"322f29a4f8","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：九十多个。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"919a862b38","type":"paragraph","text":"张：黑帮占多少？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"b4cfc408d9","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：六十三个。群众十八个。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"8ae06245f9","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政训队还存在吗？黑帮是怎么定的？这有六十多人，还有十八个人，还有工作人员，三种人。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"d702d80576","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：对。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"560a037311","type":"paragraph","text":"代表（受资产阶级反动路线迫害，被送进政训队的王××同志）：说我们是中间人物。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"8781b1a9f7","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：中间人物？（笑）","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"25947fcbc2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：中间人物和黑帮一样待遇吗？","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"83a5dffa1b","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：政治待遇上基本一样。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"5b683b4d6f","type":"paragraph","text":"张：和工作人员呢？","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"406bb39ff8","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：不一样。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"feeedc95fc","type":"paragraph","text":"张：现在这样的还有多少人？最多的时候多少人？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"f7d8b88903","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：十八个人。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"d6e3fb2e96","type":"paragraph","text":"张：软禁室怎么样？","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"92abe9b969","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表介绍软禁室情况，谈到走资派，原中控室主任景润身时）","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"47f86297a3","type":"paragraph","text":"张：他真有本领吗？技术上怎么样？","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"4529497940","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：他根本不怎么样。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"bc4f404062","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你就讲讲软禁室内幕。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"5dc58c492a","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：软禁室有多少人？","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"8d7033e525","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：八个人。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"d2c87961f1","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：控制室一共多少人？","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"4edacbb832","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：××××人。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"7d7268f814","type":"paragraph","text":"张：现在还禁闭着吗？","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e4be1b9131","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，但没有公开平反。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"826774dce6","type":"paragraph","text":"张：多久的时间？","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"f886e636f9","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：最早是八月底去的。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"2c939e1727","type":"paragraph","text":"张：其他单位还有没有软禁室？","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"6330974773","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：大楼里只有一个。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"9ddf24a725","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报有一次毛主席接见红卫兵时，电视中出现丁莱夫，《誓死纵队》一些队员欢呼）","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e1e5dc6c2d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：哪一次接见？","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"2fd2413403","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：大概第六次。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"454049e8df","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报当前运动的阻力和几个组织的情况）","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e4e71a0ea7","type":"paragraph","text":"张：誓死队有多少人？","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"120b7afd7e","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：他们说五百。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"91c73f19ed","type":"paragraph","text":"张：丁莱夫找过你们这些人开过会吗？","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"77e7f8dc8e","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，他不敢。","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a1c39d45e8","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报我局资产阶级反动路线的执行者，妄图用所谓“党纪”来镇压造反派。胡说什么“党员对党组织有意见，只有按组织系统向上一级反映，不能公开贴大字报。”代表批驳了这种谬论，并请示首长应该怎样回答这个问题。）","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"113c836ba2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你刚才已经答复了嘛！这样答复就可以。如果出了修正主义，包括党中央出了修正主义，就造他的反，不然，就要陷于苏联赫鲁晓夫式的统治。向上级控告？赫鲁晓夫的上级是谁呀？（众笑。）","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"cc200d82fa","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报传达室刚刚摘掉刘少奇的题词）","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"b78aac4eb1","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：他们想毁灭罪证嘛！专家接待室是否还挂着？","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"cedce7ab20","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：不知道。","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e21178ad31","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们大楼有多少人？","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"41469d9ee2","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：×××人。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"52ac51097f","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报政治情况）","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"098cc6c505","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政治部有多少人？你们战斗团占多少？","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"45062e13fa","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：政治部×××人，我们只有一人。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"375d9dc1d0","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们开会在剧场开？能容纳多少人？","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"61c95f9b86","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：××××人。","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"dc8361de53","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报\"一一 · 二\"事件，《誓死纵队》要首长上×楼政治部时）","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"ccd90018af","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那天非让我们到×楼去不可，气势汹汹。那天我们家里有事，不然就去了。","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"8ba79f30c5","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：后来我们要去，他们又不让去了。","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a6a642506c","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报《誓死纵队》派人到国务院告张春桥，姚文元同志的状）","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e84d07396f","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我知道。他们要找我辩论，我没理他们。","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"34ce055c4e","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报“一一·四”事件）","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"6888fcccdf","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我知道。","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"21c1210ddc","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报“一二·九”大阴谋。）","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"3743f98b95","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：可以想一想这个问题嘛！","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"1f345e3b8b","type":"paragraph","text":"（首长上车时，代表说：“欢迎首长常来”。）","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"d56ad60613","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：革命还要靠自己嘛！","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2"}],"page":{"id":"a799e2bb3b","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a100171c2","start":0,"end":0}},"yaowenyuan":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0216cf4d38","type":"paragraph","text":"张：他真有本领吗？技术上怎么样？","index":46,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"0573b42cd8","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那你们局里现在还没有选举文革委员会？","index":12,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"08261845fe","type":"paragraph","text":"代表（受资产阶级反动路线迫害，被送进政训队的王××同志）：说我们是中间人物。","index":36,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"0be35fc75a","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，但没有公开平反。","index":54,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"0e9cf772cc","type":"paragraph","text":"张：这是谁