:"7a100171c2"},{"id":"54ba15e478","type":"paragraph","text":"张：这是谁说的？丁莱夫？","index":9,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"57077e29f2","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：中间人物？（笑）","index":37,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"578dd10e94","type":"paragraph","text":"张：他真有本领吗？技术上怎么样？","index":46,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"5918a3ab13","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：×××人。","index":73,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"5b126010b5","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：就这样吧，你们说，我们听。","index":3,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"5c2f94e665","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：大概第六次。","index":61,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"6af9173408","type":"paragraph","text":"〖按：一九六六年十月十八日，《毛泽东思想战斗团》从资产阶级反动路线的白色恐怖中冲杀出来，大造梅益、丁莱夫等一小撮走资派的反。丁莱夫为了维持梅丁王朝的反动统治，扑灭革命的烈火，操纵《誓死纵队》和《红色造反团》，围剿革命派。在我们斗争最艰苦，最激烈的时刻，十二月十一日下午，毛主席司令部派张春桥、姚文元同志来我局，接见了《毛泽东思想战斗团》的十五名代表。张春桥、姚文元同志和代表们亲切交谈了三个多小时，对《毛泽东思想战斗团》的革命行动表示支持。下面是这次接见的谈话纪要。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"6df487777d","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：可以想一想这个问题嘛！","index":87,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"723ee932f3","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报局文革迫害鲁迅的儿子周海婴。当谈到有人问周海婴去南方干什么时）","index":19,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"7599940ccf","type":"paragraph","text":"张：多久的时间？","index":55,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"786b8899c0","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政治部有多少人？你们战斗团占多少？","index":75,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"7d8ce1cbda","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报有一次毛主席接见红卫兵时，电视中出现丁莱夫，《誓死纵队》一些队员欢呼）","index":59,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"7ddd5a29c2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们有没有团委呀？","index":6,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"7df3a78432","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫的“七·二九”黑报告，当谈到丁莱夫说群众批评他是“鸡蛋里头挑骨头”时）","index":8,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"7e95cd55ae","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：要不要先挨个介绍一下？","index":4,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"80529f7fa4","type":"paragraph","text":"张：现在这样的还有多少人？最多的时候多少人？","index":42,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"8390621487","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那时特别对一千二百人讲了话，说你们是受蒙蔽的，包括工作组的大多数，都是好的。我们再三讲。","index":17,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"847674ddd8","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表介绍软禁室情况，谈到走资派，原中控室主任景润身时）","index":45,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"9761f1e69c","type":"paragraph","text":"张：软禁室怎么样？","index":44,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"98bc4d1fe1","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我知道。他们要找我辩论，我没理他们。","index":83,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"9c0464ce42","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：他根本不怎么样。","index":47,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"9d9c665bb0","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报斗争梅益情况）","index":25,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a3343ed2a5","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：对。","index":10,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a4ce8eaf20","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：准备开斗争会，会议程序，口号都拟好了。","index":24,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a55ef6ff54","type":"paragraph","text":"（首长上车时，代表说：“欢迎首长常来”。）","index":88,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a5803666e9","type":"paragraph","text":"代表（受资产阶级反动路线迫害，被送进政训队的王××同志）：说我们是中间人物。","index":36,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a6f5146321","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：政治部×××人，我们只有一人。","index":76,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a7761801fa","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你就讲讲软禁室内幕。","index":48,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"a78f638fce","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：他们对周海婴采取了什么行动？","index":23,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"aa88691f95","type":"paragraph","text":"张：哪一次接见？","index":60,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"ae97912aa4","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政训队还存在吗？黑帮是怎么定的？这有六十多人，还有十八个人，还有工作人员，三种人。","index":34,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"b1d48ee822","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，但没有公开平反。","index":54,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"b2322188a9","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政训队有多少人？","index":30,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"bd65089f15","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你刚才已经答复了嘛！这样答复就可以。如果出了修正主义，包括党中央出了修正主义，就造他的反，不然，就要陷于苏联赫鲁晓夫式的统治。向上级控告？赫鲁晓夫的上级是谁呀？（众笑。）","index":68,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"c2448080e0","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报“一二·九”大阴谋。）","index":86,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"c6e39767b8","type":"paragraph","text":"张：丁莱夫找过你们这些人开过会吗？","index":65,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"cbaea98e07","type":"paragraph","text":"张：丁莱夫说他不知道周海婴是中央文革派去的。","index":22,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"cbecd14fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：政治待遇上基本一样。","index":39,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"ce03110c9d","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，我们只有联络员。","index":7,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"ce05f2c76d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我们想了解一下情况，找你们党委谈过。我们知道你们有好几个群众组织，基本上有三个，我们都想谈一下，先和你们谈。我们了解过一些情况，但不很多。你们各派都写过信。你们看有什么问题，有什么困难，打算怎么做，或者你们认为需要的，我们都想了解。","index":2,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"cef045015f","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：八个人。","index":50,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"cfd415df34","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：四天。后转入小会。","index":27,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"d56a9ca53e","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫搞假选举阴谋）","index":11,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"de066e1892","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报“一一·二”事件，《誓死纵队》要首长上×楼政治部时）","index":79,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e4cab695e7","type":"paragraph","text":"张：现在还禁闭着吗？","index":53,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e5f842eee9","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：××××人。","index":52,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"e69b3737ad","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：六十三个。群众十八个。","index":33,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"ea09d1f97c","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：他根本没有传达这些。","index":18,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"eb073ccfb8","type":"paragraph","text":"张：其他单位还有没有软禁室？","index":57,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"ee605535a9","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报传达室刚刚摘掉刘少奇的题词）","index":69,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"f191638c6b","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报当前运动的阻力和几个组织的情况）","index":62,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"f251a53b60","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，他不敢。","index":66,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"f5a0894513","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们大楼有多少人？","index":72,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"fbc56e3b7d","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报我局资产阶级反动路线的执行者，妄图用所谓“党纪”来镇压造反派。胡说什么“党员对党组织有意见，只有按组织系统向上一级反映，不能公开贴大字报。”代表批驳了这种谬论，并请示首长应该怎样回答这个问题。）","index":67,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"fc0e60d7b4","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那你们局里现在还没有选举文革委员会？","index":12,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"fc10ef7af2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：有材料可以给我们看，因为情况很多，先谈当前情况。政训队呀，软禁室呀，都是怎么回事？都解决了没有？现在还存在吗？","index":28,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"},{"id":"ffb74cbb68","type":"paragraph","text":"张：梅益开了几天会？","index":26,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2"}],"page":{"id":"6691f4de1e","publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","start":65,"end":68}}}},"__N_SSG":true}